      • setAllocationProfile

        public void setAllocationProfile(AllocationProfile allocationProfile)
        Sets an Allocation Profile for the Resource Container. Only one Allocation Profile per container is allowed. If there's already an Allocation Profile, it is replaced by the new one.
        Parameters:
        allocationProfile - is the Allocation Profile to set.
        See Also:
        AllocationProfile
